{"tid":1617221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲Melbourne 差館升支那旗同奏支那國歌","createTime":"2019-10-03T16:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:47.000Z","uid":49316,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5273ee1d9ee8d21228e06acbae6ce81af7207ed8","tid":1617221,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"俾市民屌到反艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/billbirtles/status/1179581148793458688?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbillbirtles%2Fstatus%2F1179581148793458688%3Fs%3D21&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=ca07d672\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbillbirtles%2Fstatus%2F1179581148793458688%3Fs%3D21&h=be568f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/billbirtles/status/1179581148793458688?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Box Hill ceremony has sparked strong criticism online and local councillor Blair Barker has joined the chorus.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I do find it problematic, Neil,&rdquo; he said.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;My concern is that we&rsquo;re seen to be promoting a regime that doesn&rsquo;t support the democratic values and principles such as the rule of law, and people might associate our police service with the way the police services in that regime conduct themselves.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I&rsquo;d encourage them to be a bit more judicious about the sort of flags they try to fly."},{"pid":"44aaf59a4f56085d836655abc2cb0a52bfe065c1","tid":1617221,"uid":38860,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"af3eb4d2114e94cc4e340bcdac42d4d9163a8f22","tid":1617221,"uid":62151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"右翼政府,右翼國民<br />\n竟然鳩到升中國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<b